measure.CatchLine: Requires the Housing and Community Services Department to study housing and to submit a report to the relevant interim committees of the Legislative Assembly no later than September 15, 2025.
measure.MeasureSummary:
Digest: Makes OHCS study and report on housing. (Flesch Readability Score: 78.8). 
	Requires the Housing and Community Services Department to study housing and to submit a report to the relevant interim committees of the Legislative Assembly no later than September 15, 2025.
measure.AtTheRequestOf: (at the request of House Interim Committee on Housing and Homelessness for Representative Maxine Dexter)
measure.FiscalImpact: May have fiscal impact, but no statement yet issued
measure.RevenueImpact: May have revenue impact, but no statement yet issued

historyActions.ActionText: First reading. Referred to Speaker's desk.
Referred to Housing and Homelessness with subsequent referral to Ways and Means.
